<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About - OWCS Tipping</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/global.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/interactive.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/match-cards.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/info.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <h2>
          Hello, my name is Aiden. I built this website as a personal project to combine both of my love for the
          overwatch E-sport scene and my love for programming.
        </h2>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container info-layout">
        <div>
          <h2>Why This Site Exists</h2>
          <p>
            The ability to tip on the OWCS games is something ive always wanted, but I never saw a way to do it,
            so i decided to build it myself and see how that went. Hopefully this site will keep evolving as people provide me feedback.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Built as a Student Project</h2>
          <p>
            I study a double degree in computer science and astrophysics, and I am using this project as a way to engage the skills I learnt,
            specifically the skills from computer science while still being about something I love. Due to university,
            I have limited time to work on this, and it is more of a side project, but i enjoy working on it so much.
          </p>
          <p>
            It is also a chance to build something from the ground up around a topic that is genuinely enjoyable,
            rather than just creating another generic sample app.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Project Direction</h2>
          <p>
            My long term vision for this website is for people to frequently use it to tip on the OWCS games, increasing
            the enjoyment and investment by spectators. I hope that this can help spread my passion for OWCS to others as well.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Still Growing</h2>
          <p>
            As this is still the very early stages of the project, please be patient with any bugs or things of the sort as
            I am doing my best to resolve these as I become aware of them. Please contact me when you find any issues with the page,
            or if you have suggestions to improve the experience, I would love to hear them and I am always open to feedback.
          </p>
          <p>
            Thankyou so much for taking the time to use this website as it has been such a big investment for me.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>